Pages.Text: In the center of the Obsidian Plain lies a dungeon protected by Virindi and Shadow. I hear tell that it is the path to the Singularity Caul, an island of dangers untold. I will leave you to judge your own ability to follow this path. Though I will tell you what I have been told. If you fear your death in the Singularity Bore then the Caul will see you blood run should you dare to explore.
